BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:hHSCXch71fIqbPtiiXUgo
SUMMARY:SAM Gallery Presents: Wax On
DTSTAMP:20260301T153241Z
DTSTART:20260301T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Wax On explores the methods and styles adapted by artists creat
	ing with wax. Using the ancient method of encaustic painting and process\,
	 these works feature elements of photography\, painting\, and layering com
	bined with heated wax\, pigment\, and natural tone luminosity. The artists
	 featured in this show have a nuanced understanding of this material and p
	rovide a wide range of what's possible with encaustic. Artists Larry Calki
	ns\, Nichole Dement\, Catherine Eaton Skinner\, Kathy Hastings and Joey Ro
	binson are brought together to share in the love of this multi-faceted nat
	ural medium and process. Join us for a first look and artist's reception o
	n Thursday\, February 5\, 5:30-7:30 pm.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/ev
	ents/#/details/sam-gallery-presents-wax-on/17799808/2026-03-01T00\n\nFrom 
	SEAtoday - Community & Civic
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/sam-gallery-presents-wax-
	on/17799808/2026-03-01T00
LOCATION:Seattle Art Museum\, 1300 First Avenue\, Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-community
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Community & Civic
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT7H
END:VEVENT
