	All proceeds directly support our mission to provide free\, high-quality s
	chool wardrobes to local students in need—helping them feel confident\, pr
	epared\, and ready to thrive. Join us in transforming lives\, one wardrobe
	 at a time!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/the-lives-we-
